name: Pink Dream [2020]
description: A pink dream of collaged textures, shapes, and colors. This work was created combining computer generated imagery and photographs of various textures and object from the physical world. The play of all the elements aims to create a balanced frenzy. This work is 72dpi, 9449 x 9449 pixels. Collectors in possession of this work can contact me for a full 300dpi image of the work, to be used at their discretion.
